headline: AbbVie's 10th 'Week of Possibilities' Unites Employees Across Asia for Community Impact
summary: AbbVie employees in Asia participated in the tenth Week of Possibilities (WOP), the AbbVie Foundation's annual global volunteering programme, held in June and July. This unites our employees around the world with a single purpose to serve our local communities.
